{"tid":1640901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《男兒當入樽》井上大神關注反送中文章，支人又嬲豬送助攻！","createTime":"2019-10-09T07:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T15:19:03.000Z","uid":12628,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"945b0396565412ffd2c94bd12b88ecf41875f22d","tid":1640901,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"下個抵制《男兒當入樽》<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95xS3NE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95xS3NE.jpg&h=7d9b3018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNBA 休士頓火箭隊總經理莫雷（ Daryl Morey ）日前在推特發出挺香港的貼文，引發中國大陸球迷不滿，引發抵制。沒想到日本漫畫《男兒當入樽》的作者，也被大陸網友挖出曾按讚兩則香港遊行的推文，再度引爆譁然，更有不少大陸漫迷揚言「抵制」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HhAJq05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHhAJq05.jpg&h=16189db5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲大陸網友挖出井上雄彥按讚貼文。<br />\n世界經典的籃球漫畫《男兒當入樽》作者井上雄彥，被大陸網友挖出曾關注兩篇關於香港反送中狀況的文章，分別按讚了石平太郎、河源太郎等兩位政治人物的推文，也遭大陸網友截圖轉回微博，引發怒火，更有人怒嗆作者支持港獨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZNPmzw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZNPmzw.png&h=1fdd6b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲新浪遊戲貼文。<br />\n「新浪遊戲」韋伯也轉發了這個消息，上百大陸網友也留言回應，「毅級都沒看過，巴不得不看」、「不能看就不能看，支持祖國」、「本來就不看」、「本來就是一些中二並在那捧」、「下一個 NBA 是《男兒當入樽》嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vDMHGzC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvDMHGzC.jpg&h=4699693e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲陸網友反應兩極。<br />\n但也有部分人則認為，「是什麼讓外面的人與我們不能互相理解呢？答案是牆」、「籃球之所以在中國有這地位，《男兒當入樽》貢獻排第一」、「別人本毅也是為了香港人民好，我們反對也是為了香港人民好，別搞整風擴大化行嗎？」「明明是我們被牆關起來養」"},{"pid":"39a6fded879b4b2ffa822748dfb0e897bfc2439b","tid":1640901,"uid":12628,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"正呀，神級漫畫都底制，呢班柒頭記住要有骨氣，咪撚睇男當同nba, 講都咪講，傾到咪傾！<br />\n文明世界太危險喇，支豬都係返你個豬欄乖乖等比人湯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0c098b8cb433f8c7b0a0e07ec55cbd8f71a126","tid":1640901,"uid":62815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:20:07.000Z","msg":"咁把炮自己畫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b5f41bf832fd80c83e6e0c9001db444d6d094e","tid":1640901,"uid":12628,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"bf0c098b8cb433f8c7b0a0e07ec55cbd8f71a126","tid":1640901,"uid":62815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:20:07.000Z","msg":"咁把炮自己畫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:21:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BLp953q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBLp953q.jpg&h=5caf7fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有呀人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc73701fcc6cec39ca489cab7ecffae41a8484cf","tid":1640901,"uid":52804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:23:43.000Z","msg":"井上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd63d2de82d05593039467bbe19971b914ee6b7","tid":1640901,"uid":322922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"日本come on, I love you, 一齊抗共狗"},{"pid":"57a17b98d53f0db2eaf8dc6c0c6d9bbc6931f394","tid":1640901,"uid":155088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"抵乜L嘢制，大陸西有買過正版漫畫？"},{"pid":"077aab1856c404336f9a17f0fbddddd5df38a210","tid":1640901,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"57a17b98d53f0db2eaf8dc6c0c6d9bbc6931f394","tid":1640901,"uid":155088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"抵乜L嘢制，大陸西有買過正版漫畫？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T07:34:47.000Z","msg":"唔比錢，用翻版睇翻版，佔人著數就係佢地嘅底制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointi